
Enrolment Process
1. Obtain a subscripotion from any Coin or Vaulted Object partner
2. They will return a Device Authorisation JwToken good for 48 hrs
3. Downlaod Fido Provider
https://github.com/Money-2021/PaymentClient/blob/main/Fido.dll
4.  Use the Authorisation token and Fido Provider to create the local Fido device as follows:
  // Initialise device
  Fido.FidoProvider d = new Fido.FidoProvider(authToken, true);
  d.Enrol(); // Enrol with Infastructure
  string spath = @"D:\Examples\Devices\DeviceStore-" + d.GetDeviceSin() + ".json";
  d.SaveStore(spath);

Note
1. The Auth Token is ITSDSA signed hence cannot be created outside of the infastcuture, and is validated within the Enrolment request.
